:833732,"uid":209444,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"a14807db1bef8b5558df5effcbcac666df6b71b5","tid":833732,"uid":76098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T17:03:12.000Z","msg":"其實呢d所謂&quot;病&quot; 係咪都可以追溯返個&quot;因&quot; e.g.以往傷害過自己既事"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T17:18:00.000Z","msg":"如果好正面去諗<br />\n邊緣人格（BPD）只係外觀係大人<br />\n但內心係極度渴望被愛 被重視 拒絕被拋棄既細路<br />\n<br />\n我唔知其他人係點<br />\n我係好細個個時被老母話我再喊就dump低我係超市<br />\n我嚇到邊瀨尿邊爆喊個幾分鐘<br />\n個種無助感影響我好深<br />\n類似有樣野叫adverse childhood experience<br />\n<br />\n當然成長階段都係瘋狂被拋棄<br />\n都唔識分有雞先定有蛋先<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eeec7bb26bc5e76c40fe8fe5b12f732c15e4bd74","tid":833732,"uid":209444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"95f461679c1a3cd05b0f71fcd70a5927ef79ccd9","tid":833732,"uid":55868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T17:10:28.000Z","msg":"天生係咁？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T17:19:43.000Z","msg":"所有精神病都有遺傳既可能<br />\n但我覺得自己係屋企帶比我既童年經驗 ＋ 成長階段既朋輩關係 ＋ 拍拖經歷 <br />\n幾方面都不愉快個人就崩潰"},{"pid":"8baa7b4df39124ef0b2584dd87fdf7b5dd3d675e","tid":833732,"uid":209444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f565c96b9949bb92ca2da16ead280258acaa90a1","tid":833732,"uid":141128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T17:11:19.000Z","msg":"有冇食藥？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T17:21:07.000Z","msg":"我睇開個醫生無就邊緣人格比藥我食<br />\n個人經歷覺得搵CP重有效過食藥"},{"pid":"7a1f54f87c174084812ee95958ca16fa0c5e4182","tid":833732,"uid":209444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fd5639e9320bbf0dbedbc95fa5dcc120e9a3c643","tid":833732,"uid":167007,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T17:17:31.000Z","msg":"食緊藥控制<br />\n最好唔好比我見到男人<br />\n會忍唔住溝<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T17:25:20.000Z","msg":"屌呀<br />\n我醫生無開藥比我食喎<br />\n男人<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{