ime":"2018-09-23T17:42:13.000Z","msg":"邊緣人格癲起上嚟我自己都驚<br />\n通常對朋友唔敢太癲<br />\n中學試過3人行<br />\n記得成日夾硬sip做中間分開2個fd<br />\n<br />\n不過對另一半先會病發到失控<br />\ndelete對方所有異性已經係最低級最基本<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60145e25e8e434ab3b5d491a188f2115d47ca3d4","tid":833732,"uid":191881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T17:46:40.000Z","msg":"我都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29853fe16af06240f2007daf3c268cd9a7d7ddb7","tid":833732,"uid":209444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T17:49:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/24/014739_622991163a91076bda0019886993fbc9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F24%2F014739_622991163a91076bda0019886993fbc9.jpg&h=d31f3fb8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n同病嬌都無乜分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成日幻想如果可以鎖住另一半就爽<br />\n唔洗再怕被人拋棄"}]}